metadata.description: VikitaNFT is a collection of 10,000 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain which originate from 40 well-known fiction and real-life personalities. Our goal is to create our own Metaverse, where Vikita is only the first step. Your Vikita provides an exclusive invitation to a closed community that will widen and play with new colors as our created world expands.
